contents.headline: Local club pro gets her shot at FireKeepers event

photo.caption: Adrienne Plourde is the First Assistant Golf Professional at the Battle Creek Country Club. But this weekend, Plourde is stepping away from her day job to take a chance at getting her dream job as she will play in the Symetra Tour, Road to the LPGA event - the 2015 FireKeepers Casino Hotel Championship.
